A minimalistic composition featuring a sleek smart watch face floating in empty white space, its circular screen displaying an abstract geometric pattern of intersecting colored arcs and segments representing data visualization. Beside it, a small battery icon shows a gradient fill, and a simple upward-trending line graph hovers nearby. All elements cast soft, subtle shadows suggesting they float just above the pure white background. The color palette is restrained: muted teal, warm coral, and charcoal gray against crisp white. The arrangement follows a diagonal flow from bottom-left to upper-right, creating visual movement and energy. The overall feeling is clean, modern, and instantly comprehensible—information distilled to its purest visual form.
